.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, cola, water, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, italian, colombian, pakistani, russian, american, indonesian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, biathlon, rugby, snowboarding, volleyball, sailing, climbing
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, bus, skateboard, taxi, helicopter, snowmobile, motorbike
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the pakistani##1
 3. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the italian is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the indian is on the right of the indonesian##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the russian##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the motorbike and the american##2
 9. the russian is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is cycling is the person drinking almond-milk##1
12. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the airplane##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the left of the colombian##1
14. the american is the person driving the skateboard##1
15. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the indonesian##1
16. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
17. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the colombian##1
18. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the russian##1
19. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
